---
import CameraFrame from '../components/overlays/CameraFrame';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Camera Frame Overlay</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background: #0a0a0a;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 2rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
      <h1 class="text-white text-3xl font-light mb-2 text-center">Camera Frame Variants</h1>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-center mb-12">Elige el formato que mejor se adapte a tu layout de stream</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-48 items-start">
        <!-- Default 4:3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
          <CameraFrame client:load variant="default" />
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-white font-medium">Default</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">400칑300 (4:3)</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mt-1">Cl치sico horizontal</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Wide 16:9 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
          <CameraFrame client:load variant="wide" />
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-white font-medium">Wide</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">480칑270 (16:9)</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mt-1">Pantalla ancha</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Portrait 9:16 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
          <CameraFrame client:load variant="portrait" />
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-white font-medium">Portrait</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">270칑480 (9:16)</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mt-1">Vertical para m칩vil</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Compact -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
          <CameraFrame client:load variant="compact" />
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-white font-medium">Compact</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">320칑240 (4:3)</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mt-1">Peque침o y discreto</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Square -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
          <CameraFrame client:load width={360} height={360} />
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-white font-medium">Square</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">360칑360 (1:1)</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mt-1">Formato cuadrado</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Custom vertical -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
          <CameraFrame client:load width={300} height={400} />
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-white font-medium">Custom Vertical</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">300칑400 (3:4)</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mt-1">Vertical personalizado</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Usage instructions -->
      <div class="mt-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded">
        <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-light mb-4">C칩mo usar en OBS</h2>
        <ol class="text-white/80 space-y-2 text-sm list-decimal list-inside">
          <li>Agrega una fuente de tipo <span class="text-white font-mono bg-white/10 px-1">Browser</span></li>
          <li>Usa una de estas URLs seg칰n el formato que necesites:</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-xs font-mono bg-black/30 p-4 rounded border border-white/10">
          <div class="text-white/60">Default (4:3):</div>
          <div class="text-white/90">http://localhost:4321/frames/default</div>

          <div class="text-white/60 mt-3">Wide (16:9):</div>
          <div class="text-white/90">http://localhost:4321/frames/wide</div>

          <div class="text-white/60 mt-3">Portrait (9:16):</div>
          <div class="text-white/90">http://localhost:4321/frames/portrait</div>

          <div class="text-white/60 mt-3">Compact:</div>
          <div class="text-white/90">http://localhost:4321/frames/compact</div>

          <div class="text-white/60 mt-3">Square (1:1):</div>
          <div class="text-white/90">http://localhost:4321/frames/square</div>
        </div>

        <ol start="3" class="mt-4 text-white/80 space-y-2 text-sm list-decimal list-inside">
          <li>Ajusta el ancho y alto en OBS seg칰n el tama침o del frame</li>
          <li>Marca <span class="text-white">"Shutdown source when not visible"</span> para optimizar</li>
          <li>Posiciona tu c치mara detr치s del frame en OBS</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-white/10">
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">
            游눠 <span class="text-white">Tip:</span> Aseg칰rate de ejecutar <span class="font-mono bg-white/10 px-1">npm run dev</span> para que las URLs funcionen en OBS
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
